jor+vascular+injury&amp;author=N+Kulvatunyou&amp;author=RM+Albrecht&amp;author=JS+Bender&amp;publication_year=2011&amp;journal=Am+Surg&amp;pages=534-538&amp;doi=10.1177%2F000313481107700509&amp;pmid=21679583">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">5.</div><div id="r5" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Belgers HJ, Hulsewé KW, Heeren PA, Hoofwijk AG. Traumatic abdominal wall hernia: delayed presentation in two cases and a review of the literature. <em>Hernia</em> 2005;9(4):388–391.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s10029-005-0338-6">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16237484/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Traumatic+abdominal+wall+hernia%3A+delayed+presentation+in+two+cases+and+a+review+of+the+literature&amp;author=HJ+Belgers&amp;author=KW+Hulsew%C3%A9&amp;author=PA+Heeren&amp;author=AG+Hoofwijk&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;journal=Hernia&amp;pages=388-391&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs10029-005-0338-6&amp;pmid=16237484">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Kalaci A, Karazincir S, Yanat AN. Long-standing Morel-Lavallée lesion of the thigh simulating a neoplasm. <em>Clin Imaging</em> 2007;31(4):287–291.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.clinimag.2007.01.012">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17599627/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Long-standing+Morel-Lavall%C3%A9e+lesion+of+the+thigh+simulating+a+neoplasm&amp;author=A+Kalaci&amp;author=S+Karazincir&amp;author=AN+Yanat&amp;publication_year=2007&amp;journal=Clin+Imaging&amp;pages=287-291&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.clinimag.2007.01.012&amp;pmid=17599627">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Kumar S, Hasan R, Kadavigere R, Maddukuri SB, Puppala R. Morel-Lavallee lesion (MLL) mimicking a soft tissue neoplasm. <em>J Clin Diagn Res</em> 2015;9(4):TD01–TD02. <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4437136/pdf/jcdr-9-TD01.pdf">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4437136/pdf/jcdr-9-TD01.pdf</a>. Published online April 1, 2015.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Morel-Lavallee+lesion+%28MLL%29+mimicking+a+soft+tissue+neoplasm&amp;author=S+Kumar&amp;author=R+Hasan&amp;author=R+Kadavigere&amp;author=SB+Maddukuri&amp;author=R+Puppala&amp;publication_year=2015&amp;journal=J+Clin+Diagn+Res&amp;pages=TD01-TD02">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">8.</div><div id="r8" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Sheen AJ, Stephenson BM, Lloyd DM, et al. Treatment of the sportsman’s groin: British Hernia Society’s 2014 position statement based on the Manchester Consensus Conference. <em>Br J Sports Med</em> 2014;48(14):1079–1087.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1136/bjsports-2013-092872">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24149096/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Treatment+of+the+sportsman%E2%80%99s+groin%3A+British+Hernia+Society%E2%80%99s+2014+position+statement+based+on+the+Manchester+Consensus+Co